---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SocialList from '../components/SocialList.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Mohamed Medhat" description="DevOps engineer, Linux enthusiast, and lifelong learner.">
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      Hey there! I'm <strong>Mohamed Medhat</strong> (aka Medhat), a self-taught DevOps engineer 
      from Egypt. I'm passionate about Linux, infrastructure automation, and building reliable, 
      scalable systems. I believe in learning by doing — and writing about it.
    </p>

    <p>
      Currently, I'm pursuing my B.Sc. in Computer Science at Menofia University while working on 
      hands-on projects involving Docker, Kubernetes, Ansible, and Linux system administration. 
      My goal is to join a team where I can contribute to robust infrastructure and keep growing 
      as a DevOps engineer.
    </p>

    <h2>Skills &amp; Tools</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Docker &amp; Docker Compose</li>
      <li>Kubernetes &amp; Minikube</li>
      <li>Ansible &amp; Terraform</li>
      <li>CI/CD with Jenkins</li>
      <li>Linux (Arch, RHEL, Debian)</li>
      <li>Bash &amp; Python Scripting</li>
      <li>MariaDB &amp; MySQL</li>
      <li>AWS (EC2, S3, IAM)</li>
      <li>Git &amp; GitHub</li>
      <li>LVM &amp; LUKS Encryption</li>
      <li>Networking (subnetting, routing)</li>
      <li>QEMU/KVM &amp; Virtualization</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Projects</h2>

    <p><strong>Docker Multi-Service Deployment Stack</strong><br>
    Multi-container application with MySQL, Nginx, and Flask, orchestrated via Docker Compose.</p>

    <p><strong>Kubernetes Declarative Infrastructure</strong><br>
    Kubernetes cluster with declarative YAML manifests, deployed on Minikube with AWS EBS integration.</p>

    <p><strong>Samba Active Directory Domain Controller</strong><br>
    Full AD DC using Samba 4, Kerberos, DNS, and LDAP on Ubuntu Server with Debian clients.</p>

    <p><strong>LVM-on-LUKS Encrypted Storage</strong><br>
    Full-disk encryption with LUKS and logical volume management on Arch Linux.</p>

    <h2>Grad Project</h2>
    <p>
      Built a complete Active Directory Domain Controller with Samba 4, implementing centralized 
      authentication via Kerberos, DNS/LDAP/ time sync services, LVM-based storage, 
      and AD group-based access control using SSSD and Realmd.
    </p>

    <h2>Currently Learning</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Deeper Kubernetes (Helm, operators)</li>
      <li>Advanced CI/CD pipelines</li>
      <li>Terraform &amp; IaC best practices</li>
      <li>Monitoring with Prometheus &amp; Grafana</li>
      <li>Cloud-native architecture</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
    <p>
      I'm always open to new opportunities, collaborations, or just a good tech chat. 
      Find me on:
    </p>
    <SocialList />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
